flowchart TB
    ClientA([Client A])
    ClientB([Client B])
    MS1[MS Server<br/>workspace sticky]
    MS2[MS Server<br/>workspace sticky]
    Bus[(Pub/Sub Bus<br/>per-workspace<br/>channel topics)]
    Persist[Persist Service]
    Messages[(Messages Store<br/>partition by channel)]
    Search[(Search Index<br/>per workspace)]
    Notif[Notification Service]

    ClientA <-->|WebSocket| MS1
    ClientB <-->|WebSocket| MS2
    MS1 --> Bus
    MS2 --> Bus
    Bus --> MS1
    Bus --> MS2
    Bus --> Persist
    Persist --> Messages
    Persist -.-> Search
    Persist -.->|push if offline| Notif

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class ClientA,ClientB external
    class MS1,MS2,Persist,Notif service
    class Bus,Messages,Search store
